flowchart TD
  A[Signed-in publisher edits or creates public content] --> B[Submit publish form]
  B --> C{Content would become public?}
  C -- No --> D[Save without publishing agreement gate]
  C -- Yes --> E[PublicVisibilityGate checks content publishing agreement]
  E --> F{Already accepted?}
  F -- Yes --> G[Save succeeds]
  F -- No --> H[Render form error with modal launch link]
  H --> I[Publisher opens content publishing agreement modal]
  I --> J[Turbo frame loads seeded agreement page]
  J --> K[Direct-accept footer shows Cancel and I agree]
  K --> L{Scrolled through full agreement?}
  L -- No --> M[I agree stays disabled]
  L -- Yes --> N[I agree becomes enabled]
  N --> O[POST /agreements/:id/accept]
  O --> P[Acceptance recorder stores publish_modal consent]
  P --> Q[Modal closes and launch button changes to Accepted]
  Q --> R[Publisher re-submits form]
  R --> G
